item.title: Python Packages
item.description: Python Packages # NijiGPen's functionality relies on some third-party Python packages, which have to be separately downloaded and installed. If you have no experience with Blender add-ons that have similar requirements, it is strongly suggested to read this page before using the add-on. Dependency Summary # The table below lists the packages required for each type of operation. Lacking a package will not affect operations that do not require it.
